item.title: what is you?
item.description: There is going to have the first Dark ID (DID) design. The idea of DID dwelled in my mind for about two years. Now I can finally see its form. I am not sure how others receive it but it’s mine, unique to what I am. This reminds me of one thing that Jorge Borges said in Spanish. “Sólo perduran en el tiempo las cosas Que no fueron del tiempo.” After translation, it is roughly as follows: Only things that were not of time endure in time.
